{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n<body><p>更新時間：14:51 2026-05-02 HKT<br/>發佈時間：14:51 2026-05-02 HKT</p>\n<p>發佈時間：14:51 2026-05-02 HKT</p><img alt=\"救援人員到場搜索失蹤事主。楊偉亨攝\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4cae3fd3f4ee2a938c07de4994d07c56/2026-05/KakaoTalk_20260502_143723509_11.jpg\"/><p>今(2日)早上11時半，一名男子報案指其28歲胞弟，昨晚與女友發生爭執後離家，至今失聯，透過GPS發現他走到黃大仙沙田坳道，恐他尋死，於是報警求助。救援人員在法藏寺集合上山尋找事主蹤影，惟暫未有發現。</p><img alt=\"楊偉亨攝\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bb5bbf2af56407b9da07df031650284c/2026-05/KakaoTalk_20260502_143723509_01.jpg\"/><img alt=\"山坡附近發現啤酒罐與煙頭。楊偉亨攝\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d78b8adea23d104af613576eeade5de3/2026-05/KakaoTalk_20260502_143723509_03.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3b3c6dd47bfd40c681185da4ea30869e/2026-05/KakaoTalk_20260502_143723509_05.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/98f17d51d9a2a703efdb07d070353f11/2026-05/KakaoTalk_20260502_143723509_06.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fce23ac32e97aa3abf0782dacc4aaf63/2026-05/KakaoTalk_20260502_143723509_09.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/df32144050e1ac8a4f79017e80449890/2026-05/KakaoTalk_20260502_143723509_10.jpg\"/><img alt=\"救援人員上山搜索。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cd87d2a42aff18c581af020de884d5b0/2026-05/KakaoTalk_20260502_143723509_12.jpg\"/><p>消防搜索附近山坡期間，檢獲懷疑為事主遺下的啤酒罐及煙頭。</p><p>最Hit</p>\n</body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-02T07:21:44.346754+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":212,"images":8,"source":"星島頭條","fallback":"none"}}